                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>The article reports that Gen. Scholfield appointed Maj. H. B. Burnham Judge
                    of the Hustings Court of Richmond last Monday; Burnham replaces Judge William H.
                    Lyons, who died.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
