                <summary>In his letter, "Civis" nominates J. M. Hanger, Y. H. Peyton, and James
                    Bumgardner as delegates to the convention. The three men "combine in themselves
                    vigor of intellect, fluency, and eloquence in debate, and boldness and decision
                    of action."</summary>
                <note/>
